{"tid":2414974,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"媒體:曼城想要梅西 曼城:我冇撚講過要喎","createTime":"2021-02-20T00:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T04:17:19.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e887fafafdff083fa21d872dfbd60a6cfa3058ce","tid":2414974,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T00:23:07.000Z","msg":"曼城闢謠4.3億鎊報價美斯：雙方無任何談判！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2021/02/19/b/b99a19cb781ee5e4caf3683e471f3b67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2021%2F02%2F19%2Fb%2Fb99a19cb781ee5e4caf3683e471f3b67.jpg&h=1ec8ca98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曼城闢謠報價美斯<br />\n<br />\n  近日英國媒體《太陽報》披露，曼城給美斯（Lionel Messi）開出一份總價為4.3億英鎊的5年合約，但曼城方面很快就對此進行闢謠。<br />\n<br />\n  《天空體育》和《BBC》都對曼城的闢謠做出報導，曼城內部的消息人士向他們表示，有關曼城給美斯報價的報導是子虛烏有，不管是夏窗還是冬窗，從美斯離隊新聞被曝出開始，曼城都沒有給美斯報價過，目前雙方沒有進行過任何談判。"},{"pid":"683bd880d685d922ee5cd0960dd64c131e42dc27","tid":2414974,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T00:42:51.000Z","msg":"5年合約吹大咗"},{"pid":"67278a8b24461d47de33aeb1b748a87fb396b8e4","tid":2414974,"uid":195915,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T00:44:02.000Z","msg":"咁撚廢要黎做咩？"},{"pid":"597dc74d12d358b924b8b7a9449012e2e318fbdd","tid":2414974,"uid":86316,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T00:47:45.000Z","msg":"同牙路續約先好過啦"},{"pid":"263ac758c0a50ba57f2f220a1430375461935f56","tid":2414974,"uid":37723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T00:51:35.000Z","msg":"Go MU la diu"},{"pid":"71341bccbde48793dba417dba4e6091a4270b091","tid":2414974,"uid":45518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T01:46:30.000Z","msg":"而家嘅曼城唔會想要美C牙朗呢啲上一世代嘅產物啦"},{"pid":"c550bca149792a1492c08f5f6f688b31cb170457","tid":2414974,"uid":11914,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T01:49:30.000Z","msg":"上年錯過左，依家冇人要<img src=\"/assets/